longBusinessSummary: Websol Energy System Limited manufactures and sells solar photovoltaic (PV) cells and modules in India. The company was formerly known as Websol Energy Systems Ltd. and changed its name to Websol Energy System Limited in October 2011. Websol Energy System Limited was incorporated in 1990 and is based in Falta, India.
